            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"half-the-sky-half-the-seats\">Half the Sky, Half the Seats?</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Women's share of seats in national parliaments, earliest available year (~1997) vs 2024, for 25 countries. Rwanda leads at 61%. Japan and India remain below 16%.</span></span>"
